<p>Dear <%= @recipient %>,</p>
<p>Congratulations on depositing your work via Libra, the University of Virginia's scholarly repository.</p>

<% if @embargo_release_date.present? %>
<p>The title and abstract for the work "<%= @title %>" will be available for immediate access. After your embargo ends on <%= date_formatter(@embargo_release_date) %>, the files for "<%= @title %>" will be available for <%= @visibility_after_embargo %> access.
<% else %>
<p>The work "<%= @title %>"" will be available immediately for <%= @visibility %> access.
<% end %>

<p>You have opted to grant to users of your work the following re-use rights: <%= @rights_name %>.</p>
<p>The permanent location for your work (the DOI) is <a href="<%= @doi_url %>"><%= @doi_url %></a>.</p>
<p>Always provide this exact link when sharing your work with colleagues, collaborators, and on social media.
<strong>If your work did not receive a DOI (e.g. there is no link above), please contact us immediately at</strong> <%= MAIL_SENDER %>.</p>
